IoT Components Required for Continuous Health Monitoring System

1. ESP32 (for Wi-Fi & IoT connectivity)
2. MAX30100/MAX30102 (Heartbeat sensor)
3. MPX5050GP/BMP180 (Blood pressure sensor)
4. DHT11/DS18B20 (Temperature sensor)
5. ADXL345/MPU6050 (Accelerometer for fetal movements)
6. SIM800L/SIM900A (GSM module for SMS alerts)
7. OLED Display (128x64 I2C)
8. AD8232 ECG Sensor â€“ Captures ECG signals
